stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> AgentExecution: crew.kickoff()

    AgentExecution --> DAGBuild: Output received
    DAGBuild --> LoopCheck: DAG node added

    LoopCheck --> ConstitutionCheck: CONTINUE\nsimilarity < 0.85
    LoopCheck --> LoopDetected: LOOP_DETECTED\nsimilarity >= 0.85
    LoopCheck --> MaxIterExceeded: MAX_ITERATIONS_EXCEEDED
    LoopCheck --> TimedOut: TIMEOUT\nelapsed > max_duration

    LoopDetected --> [*]: Execution halted
    MaxIterExceeded --> [*]: Execution halted
    TimedOut --> [*]: Execution halted

    ConstitutionCheck --> ASTVerification: PASS\n0 hard violations
    ConstitutionCheck --> Blocked: Hard rule violated

    Blocked --> [*]: No attestation generated

    ASTVerification --> SupervisorScore: score > 0\nno blocked imports
    ASTVerification --> ASTFailed: Blocked import\nor unsafe call

    ASTFailed --> [*]: Attestation rejected

    SupervisorScore --> Z3Proofs: ACCEPT\nS >= 7.0
    SupervisorScore --> Retry: RETRY\n5.0 <= S < 7.0
    SupervisorScore --> Escalated: ESCALATE\nS < 5.0

    Retry --> AgentExecution: crew_factory rebuild\nfresh providers

    Escalated --> [*]: Terminal failure

    Z3Proofs --> RedBlueProtocol: 4/4 theorems verified

    RedBlueProtocol --> GovernedMemory: Issues resolved\nACR computed
    RedBlueProtocol --> Unresolved: No deterministic evidence

    Unresolved --> GovernedMemory: Logged with warnings

    GovernedMemory --> CertificateSigning: Bi-temporal write\nconstitutional decay applied

    CertificateSigning --> ComplianceGate: BLAKE3 hash\nHMAC-SHA256 signature

    ComplianceGate --> MerkleBatch: GCR = 1.0\nCOMPLIANT
    ComplianceGate --> NoAttestation: GCR < 1.0\nNON_COMPLIANT

    NoAttestation --> [*]: No on-chain trace

    MerkleBatch --> PostgreSQL: Certificate queued\nor batch flushed

    PostgreSQL --> EnigmaScanner: dof_trust_scores\nINSERT ~900ms

    EnigmaScanner --> AvalanchePublish: combined_trust_view\nupdated

    AvalanchePublish --> OnChainConfirmed: registerAttestation()\n~2-3s confirmation

    OnChainConfirmed --> [*]: 3-layer verification complete
